Playing quantum werewolves in times of covid 19.


> instructions for running the thing
Have python 2.7 and npm installed.

$ git clone <this repo>
$ cd quantum-wolves-online/node
$ npm install

> run using
$ npm start
then have your players point their browsers at http://[your-machine]:2567/01-chat.html

> instructions for using the thing
basic instructions included atop the interface.
some fancy instructions are over at
https://github.com/verhoevenv/bra-ket-wolf

there is exactly one game room per instance of the server.
bra-ket wolves is apparently limited to 10-11 or so players

> troubleshooting
Things don't work? try disabling your adblocker/tracker blocker


Networking code is adapted from
https://github.com/colyseus/colyseus-examples

Quantum werewolves code is adapted from
https://github.com/verhoevenv/bra-ket-wolf


